title: Flight Simulator 2020 - World Update IV - Rotterdam The Hague Airport (EHRD)
description:
In this video we will look at the Rotterdam The Hague Airport and the sceneries around it. The focus is on the parts which have been updated as part of World Update IV: France/Benelux which has been released today. We are using the drone mode in this case so sit back and relax and enjoy this video.
